OL,6,W"###########################!         !
OL,7,MSinclair C5 Restoration                
OL,9,BI was looking around for a project with
OL,10,Ba mechanical element, as I usually     
OL,11,Brepair old electronics. Walking through
OL,12,BLondon I came across a beautifully     
OL,13,Brestored DeLorean - complete with all  
OL,14,Bthe 'Back to the Future' conversions.  
OL,15,FA project like this has great appeal   
OL,16,Fbut at around #30,000 and without any  
OL,17,Fknowledge about cars I decided I needed
OL,18,Fa more manageable project, so I decided
OL,19,Fa Sinclair C5 would fit the bill.      
OL,20,EAlso, like 'Back to the Future' the C5 
OL,21,Ecame out in the summer of 1985!        
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
