OL,6,W"###########################!         !
OL,7,MPart 1 - Vehicle Check Over            
OL,9,BIn this video I investigate how to go  
OL,10,Babout buying a C5, check over the      
OL,11,Bvehicle, and then take it out for a    
OL,12,Bquick test ride.                       
OL,13,FI bought my C5 from eBay for #420 plus 
OL,14,Fvan hire as it wouldn't fit in my car. 
OL,15,FYou should also check out Gumtree and  
OL,16,FThe "Sinclair C5 Owners Group" on      
OL,17,FFacebook as you may get a better deal. 
OL,18,EIf you want a working machine you      
OL,19,Eshould check the "pod" works as this   
OL,20,Econtains a microchip that is hard to   
OL,21,Ereplace if it is faulty.               
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
