OL,6,W"###########################!         !
OL,7,MPart 2 - Vehicle Strip down            
OL,9,BIn the second video I undertake a      
OL,10,Bcomplete strip down to the bare        
OL,11,Bchassis.                               
OL,12,FOne of the reasons I wanted to film    
OL,13,Fthe tear down was to help the C5 novice
OL,14,Fsuch as myself.                        
OL,15,EI took over 100 screenshots and        
OL,16,Eproduced a step-by-steo guide that can 
OL,17,Ebe printed and taken to the workshop   
OL,18,Eor garage. This is available on my     
OL,19,Ewebsite at www.retroworkshop.uk        
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
