OL,6,W"###########################!         !
OL,7,MPart 3 - Rebuild                       
OL,9,BThe Lotus designed chassis was sent to 
OL,10,Ba local firm where it was bead blasted 
OL,11,Band powder coated, and looks as good   
OL,12,Bas new.                                
OL,13,FThe vehicle body was scrubbed with Cif 
OL,14,Fand a scouring pad to remove dirt and  
OL,15,Fstains.                                
OL,16,EI sanded and spray painted the other   
OL,17,Emetal parts such as forks and steering 
OL,18,Ebar.Then the C5 was re-assembled and   
OL,19,Efresh grease applied to all the        
OL,20,Ebearings. A new set of tires and tubes,
OL,21,Eand new decals completed the job.      
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
