OL,5,WjQ+/+'"-'*%/*%/(.'*%/"-'*% W5+9S#+/'Wle
OL,6,W"###########################!         !
OL,7,MPart 4 - Electrics                     
OL,9,BThe C5 was marketed as an "electric    
OL,10,Bvehicle" so it was fitting to dedicate 
OL,11,Ba video to the electricals.            
OL,12,FI take you on a tour of the vehicle    
OL,13,Felectrics using my "C5 Simulator".     
OL,14,EI then strip and service the motor,    
OL,15,Efit a safety wiring loom to make it    
OL,16,Eeasier to remove the battery. I fit a  
OL,17,Enew leisure battery and undertake some 
OL,18,Emodifications to the "pod" to make it  
OL,19,Eless prone to damage.                  
OL,20,AThe finished C5 goes for a ride around 
OL,21,AMK with some fancy aerial filming.     
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
